`rabbitAdmin` itself is a mock object, that means every method has default behaviour to return `null`. If you have not specified any behavior for `rabbitAdmin.getQueueProperties(anyString())` or `rabbitAdmin.getQueueProperties(&quot;responseQueueName&quot;)`, then this call will return `null`.

Then you have the next part:

