        .get(&quot;QUEUE_MESSAGE_COUNT&quot;)

If you don&#39;t have any behaviour specified, then you are calling partically `null.get(&quot;QUEUE_MESSAGE_COUNT&quot;)` which will get you your `NullPointerException`.


